<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>     I am coming back to EQ after a year off and am deciding on a new character choice.  I had a druid up to 24, it was pretty cool, but got kind of boring.  From what I've seen of this forum, including high end pet hammer and summoned weapons, this class looks like a lot of fun.  I would enjoy healing my allies , but it looks as though Clerics offer even more with nice hp an AC.  Are they semi-soloable at low levels?  Would appreciate any response or offered advice.  Thanks</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td><td align="right" class="fs8" >5 replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
