<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>That is misinformation. Clerics DO NOT receive a 3% experience penalty. <br /> <br />There USED to be class based exp penalties, but they were for hybrid classes (such as paladin or SK), and they have been removed. There ARE race based penalties and bonuses. For example, iksar and troll get an EXP penalty. Halflings get an EXP bonus.  <br /> <br />I believe there are a few other rece modifiers, but I don't remember which other reces. <br /> <br />But no cleric penalty, zip, none at all. <br /> <br />And the heal bonus a cleric gets is 5% above the listed HP of the heal, not 3%. That is an inherent class bonus, and has no impact on experience.</p>
